Multi-Tenant SaaS Backend Scaffold
Design a production-ready multi-tenant architecture with row-level security, tenant isolation, and resource quotas. Implement JWT authentication with refresh tokens, role-based access control with permissions, and audit logging. Support tenant-specific configurations, background job processing with BullMQ, and feature flags. Use Prisma with PostgreSQL row-level security.

Key Features: Strict null checks enforcement, readonly properties for immutability, private class fields, decorators for authorization, namespace merging for plugin system, module augmentation for extending third-party types

